# Screenshots Directory

Place your submission screenshots here:

- `admin-dashboard.png` - Screenshot of /admin page showing metrics
- `vault-setup.png` - (Optional) Screenshot of vault creation
- `transaction-flow.png` - (Optional) Screenshot of payment flow
- `approvals-page.png` - (Optional) Screenshot of pending approvals

## How to Capture Screenshots

1. Navigate to https://stellar-pay-cross-border-remittance-hub.vercel.app/admin
2. Wait for metrics to load with real user data
3. Take a full-page screenshot
4. Save as `admin-dashboard.png` in this directory
5. Update README.md to reference the screenshot
